Description: We at The Mentis Company strive to facilitate a healthier space for all. Our mission is to ensure everyone feels protected and healthy
Headquarters Regions: Western US
Full Description: We at The Mentis Company strive to facilitate a healthier space for all. As COVID-19 evidently changes the world, our mission is to ensure everyone feels protected and healthy at all times when they leave their homes. As the first to come out with this product, we've worked diligently to create something that makes a true impact on your life and the lives of your loved ones. As we continue to expand our brand, we remain committed to respecting our values and providing an alternative lifestyle of being mindful and seeking better when it comes to what we put on and in our bodies. As the world continues to navigate the most health-sensitive year in history, the question plaguing our minds is how cautious we can be to protect ourselves. When the COVID-19 crisis started, it became clear that the ingredients we use every day need to be evaluated for not only effectiveness but overall health safety. With everyone creating more and more products to be used in the fight against disease and germs, we at The Mentis Company took a different approach in the way we selected ingredients for our customers. About six months into the pandemic, supplies were running out in the stores, and we were forced to get creative when it came to sanitizing. But when we went through the common items needed to make the typical sanitizing cleansers, many of them became unappealing when you looked at how toxic they are, especially when you begin to breathe in those chemicals. So, we took matters into our own hands and set our sights on curating a cleanser that helps without harm. With extensive research, we landed on a key component that works for the skin in ways that harsh chemicals cannot. As the world continues to navigate the most health-sensitive year in history, the question plagued how cautious we can be to protect ourselves. While the year 2020 was underway, it became clear that the ingredients we use every day need to be evaluated for not only effectiveness but overall safety health. With everyone creating more and more products to be used to fight against disease and germs at The Mentis Company, we took a different approach in the way we selected ingredients for our customers.

While completing their graduate studies at the University of Washington, the two met Dr. Aaron Falk, a PhD physicist with a specialization in optical systems, who developed the underlying technology for BodyKey. The company's initial product, BodyKey, gives weight-loss seekers an immediate reading of how much fat they have burned from their diet and fitness efforts. This information provides a huge psychological boost for keeping people motivated since they can now see that they are, in fact, making progress towards their weight loss goals. Additionally, the accompanying computer software program is packed with useful tools that allow the user to track their daily progress, help them select foods and exercise programs that are ideal for their body, and provide them with accurate forecasting so they will know how long it will take them to reach their weight loss goal.
